   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2007_sterope-2" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant Sterope$<BR>Being too beautiful is a problem.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Go to Vernicka.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What are you talking about…</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Vernicka sighs loudly.)</FONT> If you want to die so much, you can just hang yourself. I don't understand why you keep choosing the difficult path.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Who is Mahan?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I heard everything. So Child Mahan involved? Why Mahan of all people?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Child Mahan is not as famous as Tryan but he's a typical Child -- curious and arrogant. He thinks he is clever and cunning. That would do disservice to him one day but sad to say not for now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>He has a bad reputation.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Anyway, he's a dirty hedonist who loves fun. He is looking for fun things here since the Childs have swarmed here because of the Monolith's door. Although he's not trying to take over Merca, we don't know what might happen if he becomes the only crazy dog in this area. So I was thinking of ways to get rid of him.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>The tiger is gone and now a fox is... well, mad dog would be a better word. After Tryan's death, a mad dog is roaming around Merca and there's no reason for me to view it kindly.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-e" image="QN_lapis.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-f" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Lapis?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I think it's time to start supporting Lapis who is trying to become the new boss of the Thieves.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2-f" image="QN_lapis.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Yeah. If he can make his own kingdom of thieves, it would be good for him and good for us too. First, you should go and meet him.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3" image="QW_111.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I'm keeping contact with Lapis at <FONT color=#a82424>Retrograde Highland</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2042_lapis-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2042_lapis-3-a" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Long time no see. </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>My saviour, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. I didn't expect you to come.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2042_lapis-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2042_lapis-3-b" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>To see you here at such a time... Did you come under President Vernicka's orders?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2042_lapis-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2042_lapis-3-c" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What do you mean?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>I see. Then you must have heard that we're going to take a step further from simple spy missions to taking over the Thieves. Though it was not on our own will.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2042_lapis-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2042_lapis-3-d" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>Though the boss of the Thieves died, I was only one of the underbosses. I didn't have the intention of becoming the boss. It would make it harder for me to conceal my identity and also, another underboss has been acting strangely lately.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2042_lapis-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2042_lapis-3-e" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>One of the underbosses whom I have never even seen before has joined hands with the Childs and is trying to take over the Thieves. Those of us who are against it and the other underbosses have started to form an alliance.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2042_lapis-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2042_lapis-3-f" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>The Childs are directly interfering with the Thieves now...?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>One of the other underbosses is the candidate for the next boss but I could become the candidate anytime. We need to observe the situation and take control of the Thieves by ourselves. That's why I requested aid from Vernicka.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2042_lapis-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n2042_lapis-4" mid="43" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>There were many Childs who took interest in the Thieves and the Goldstone Tears even in the past. The ex-boss was trading directly with Tryan. But there was never such a cunning and explicit intervention from them. That caught us by surprise.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n2042_lapis-4" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Lapis$<BR>We can't lose. I can't lose my kingdom again.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Go back to Vernicka.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4-a" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>You're back. So the Childs are intervening directly with the Thieves? Could it be him?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4-b" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>(Receive Reward)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-4-!next" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>It's understandable if he's the one who's behind this. All we can do is to have faith in Lapis.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
